# Secrets never belong in the image — production reads Fly secrets from the
# environment. A bare ".env.local" would only match the context root, and
# `COPY frontend/ ./` would still carry frontend/.env.local into the build
# stage, so match at any depth.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example